{
  "stem": "12491.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Russian soldiers, with their big lantern, opening every door and looking in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And while they were looking in, they found nobody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I hoped that they're not going to come to our train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Maybe they get tired of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they did, and they saw us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there were about six different military with their rifles like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We are spies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] I spoke and understood a little Russian at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We are spies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And one of them jumped into-- I think it was like a sergeant-- and I was prepared for him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I have to now backtrack a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When we delivered all these weapons which we took from the Germans and stored them in Schindler's camp after the war, we got-- 18 of us-- 28 of us, got a special paper, handwritten by a Russian general who was in charge of the Ukrainian front.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And on the bottom of it was a very peculiar triangular stamp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the stamp said, Kommandant of the Ukrainian Front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When that guy came into the thing, I handed to him two bottles of whiskey, and I showed him this paper.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I had that paper.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he started yelling at the others, I have a pass-- that the guy has a pass.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He stuck the bottles of whiskey into his pants and walked out and told them, he's okay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They have a pass.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They can go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So, and, and another way to be lucky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We eventually wound up, wound up in Russia-- I'm sorry, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I'm sorry, I know the camera is going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We wound up in Austria.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
